---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Research Workflow Guidebook
description: 언어를 선택하고, LaTeX부터 GitHub 협업까지 이어지는 연구 워크플로우를 시작하세요.
lang: ko
langSwitch:
  url: /
  label: English
pageClass: page-landing
---
<main>
  <section class="landing-hero">
    <div class="wrap hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-copy-block">
        <h1>설치부터 GitHub 협업까지 이어지는 연구 워크플로우를 구축하세요.</h1>
        <p class="hero-copy">
          LaTeX, VS Code, Git, GitHub를 활용하는 연구자를 위한 가이드북입니다. 환경 설치부터 일상적인 작성 루프, 저장소 협업까지 단계별로 정리했습니다.
        </p>
        <div class="button-row">
          <a class="button button-secondary" href="/">English</a>
          <a class="button button-primary" href="/ko/">한국어</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="hero-panel panel">
        <p class="eyebrow">Recent Updates</p>
        {% if updates.currentBuild %}
          <h2 class="hero-panel-title">{{ updates.currentBuild.title }}</h2>
        {% endif %}
        <dl class="updates-list">
          {% for item in updates.completed %}
            {% if loop.index <= 2 %}
              <div>
                <dt>{{ item.date }}</dt>
                <dd>
                  {% if item.url %}
                    <a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.title }}</a>
                  {% else %}
                    {{ item.title }}
                  {% endif %}
                </dd>
              </div>
            {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
        </dl>
        <a class="text-link" href="/updates/">More updates →</a>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="editorial-band">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2>Route Map</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        {% for section in navigation.sections %}
          <a class="feature-card panel" href="{{ section.url.ko }}">
            <div class="card-logo-row">
              {% if section.key == "start-here" %}
                <img class="card-logo" src="/assets/images/LaTeX_project_logo_bird.svg.png" alt="LaTeX">
                <img class="card-logo" src="/assets/images/Visual_Studio_Code_1.35_icon.svg.png" alt="VS Code">
              {% elif section.key == "writing-in-vs-code" %}
                <img class="card-logo" src="/assets/images/Visual_Studio_Code_1.35_icon.svg.png" alt="VS Code">
              {% elif section.key == "git-github" %}
                <img class="card-logo" src="/assets/images/Visual_Studio_Code_1.35_icon.svg.png" alt="VS Code">
                <img class="card-logo" src="/assets/images/GitHub-Mark.png" alt="GitHub">
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            <p class="card-kicker">{{ section.kicker.ko }}</p>
            <h3>{{ section.title.ko }}</h3>
            <p>{{ section.summary.ko }}</p>
          </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
